_sText:
This is the first map I've actually managed to finish. 
(I keep coming up with new ideas and making new maps without finishing the older ones hahaha.)
Anyway, this map holds a maximum of 32 players but I recommend you have some where between 12-24 players at most.
I tested the map with bots and it works out well and very fast paced.
If you have any information or tips that I could use to improve this map or any maps I make in the future, please share it with me. Thanks and I hope you enjoy the map.
